<tr>
<th align="center"><img src="room2.jpg"  height="300" width="850" /></th></td>

<tr>  <td align="center"><font color="#ffffff"><big><b>We are Here<br />
It's a room full of words and pictures organized to please, surprise,<br /> and sometimes to educate. It is a place to ask questions and <br />find answers; a place to chat, whether on keyboard or face to face. <br />It is your library -- Come and visit<br /><br /><br /><br /></td></tr></big></b>

</table> 





